\c 3
\s Kudzoka kwaKristu
\p
\v 1 Tsamba iyi yechipiri, vadikanwi ndinokunyorerai ikozvino; panaidzedzi dzose \add mbiri\add* ndinomutsa ndangariro dzenyu paku\add ku\add*yeuchidzai,
\v 2 kuti murangarire mashoko akambotaurwa nevaporofita vatsvene, nemurairo wedu tiri vaapasitori vaIshe neMuponesi;
\v 3 Muchiziva ichi pakutanga, kuti kuchauya pamazuva ekupedzisira vanongoseka, vachifamba maererano neruchiva rwavo,
\v 4 uye vachiti: Chiripi chivimbiso chekuuya kwake? Nekuti kubva zvarara madzibaba zvinhu zvose zvakangodaro sepakutanga kwekusikwa.
\v 5 Nekuti ichi havazivi maune, kuti matenga aivapo kubva kare, nenyika iripo kubva mumvura, \add yakaitwa\add* nemvura neshoko raMwari;
\v 6 nazvo nyika yaivapo nguva iyo yakafukidzwa nemvura ikaparadzwa.
\v 7 Asi matenga nenyika zviripo ikozvino zvakachengeterwa moto neshoko iroro pazuva rekutongwa nerekuparadzwa kwevanhu vasingadi Mwari.
\v 8 Asi chinhu chimwe ichi ngachirege kusazikanwa nemwi vadiwa, kuti zuva rimwe kuna She \add ra\add*kaita samakore ane churu, nemakore churu sezuva rimwe.
\v 9 Ishe wechivimbiso haanonoki, sezvinoreva vamwe vachiti kunonoka; asi moyo murefu kwatiri, asingadi kuti vamwe vaparare asi kuti vose vasvike pakutendeuka.
\v 10 Asi zuva raIshe richauya sembavha usiku, naro matenga achapfuura nekutinhira kukuru, nezvekutanga zvichanyunguduswa nekupisa kukuru, nenyika nemabasa ari mairi achapiswa.
\v 11 Sezvo zvinhu izvi zvose zvichaparadzwa, imwi munofanira kuva vanhu vakadiniko pamafambiro matsvene nekunamata Mwari,
\v 12 makatarisira nekudokwairira kusvika kwezuva raMwari; naro matenga ari mumoto achaparadzwa, nezvekutanga zvinyunguduke nekupisa kukuru.
\v 13 Asi sechivimbiso chake, tinotarisira matenga matsva nenyika itsva, munogara kururama mazviri.
\v 14 Saka vadiwa, zvamunotarisira zvinhu zvakadaro, shingairai kuti muwanikwe naye murugare, musina gwapa uye musingamhuriki.
\v 15 Mugoti moyo murefu waIshe wedu ruponeso, hama yedu inodikanwa Pauro sezvaakakunyoreraiwo zvichienderana nenjere dzakapiwa kwaari;
\v 16 sezvaanotaura mutsamba \add dzake\add* dzose maererano nezvinhu izvi; madziri mune zvimwe zvikukutu kunzwisisika; izvo avo vasina kudzidza nevasina kusimba vanozviminamisa, nemamwe magwaro, zvive kuparadzwa kwavo.
\v 17 Naizvozvo imwi, vadikanwi, zvamagara muchiziva, chenjerai kuti muregewo kutsauswa nekunyengera kwevakaipa, muwe pakusimba kwenyu.
\v 18 Asi kurai munyasha neparuzivo rwaIshe wedu neMuponesi Jesu Kristu. Rukukudzo \add ngaruende\add* kwaari ikozvino nekusingeperi. Ameni.
